data.description: This 4-bedroom, 1-bathroom home at 1237 5th Ave is an ideal choice for those seeking a comfortable and welcoming residence in Newport. Its classic charm, combined with modern functionality, creates a timeless appeal.  Upgrades include: new carpet main level 2020, new roof in 2023, New garage doors 2022, New AC in 2022, High efficiency water heater in 2022, new washer & dryer 2018. With main level laundry, this home offers single level living. Situated on a large corner lot with mature trees, close to Mississippi River, schools, parks and restaurants and easy access to Hwy 61.
